{"title":"Podcast #102 – Cannondale Factory Racing & Lefty Deep Dive","link":"https://bikerumor.com/podcast-102-cannondale-factory-racing-lefty-deep-dive/","date":1722008913000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cannondale-lefty-podcast-interview-PROMO-1-1-1536x1024.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"cannondale-lefty-podcast-interview\" /></p>\n<p>Jordan sits down and talks about all things Lefty with Cannondale Factory Racing (CFR) and the suspension team at Cannondale. Steve Exstance, Murray Washburn, and Lefty Larry walk us through the conception, progression, and even electrification of Cannondale’s Lefty line. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LeftyLarry_BikeRumor_2.jpeg\"><img width=\"1087\" height=\"723\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LeftyLarry_BikeRumor_2.jpeg\" alt=\"LeftyLarry_BikeRumor_2\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LeftyLarry_BikeRumor_2.jpeg 1087w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LeftyLarry_BikeRumor_2-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LeftyLarry_BikeRumor_2-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LeftyLarry_BikeRumor_2-768x511.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LeftyLarry_BikeRumor_2-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/LeftyLarry_BikeRumor_2-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Lefty Larry with his collection of period-correct Cannondale Race machines. All images: Cannondale) </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Larry was kind enough to meet us at CFR headquarters. He described “a day in the life at CFR,” explaining what team members do and how all the moving parts behind wins work together. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Murray_Washburn_BikeRumor-2.jpg\"><img width=\"1632\" height=\"1224\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Murray_Washburn_BikeRumor-2.jpg\" alt=\"Murray_Washburn_BikeRumor 2\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Murray_Washburn_BikeRumor-2.jpg 1632w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Murray_Washburn_BikeRumor-2-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Murray_Washburn_BikeRumor-2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Murray_Washburn_BikeRumor-2-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Murray_Washburn_BikeRumor-2-768x576.jpg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Murray talking in the pits with the Cannondale Factory Race Team </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We cover how the team dials in their suspension for different course demands and rider styles and what it’s like servicing multiple Lefties while traveling worldwide. Plus, we get the insider scoop and some secret tips from Lefty Larry for setup, lockout and the team answers reader questions. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_3-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"2304\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_3-1536x2304.jpg\" alt=\"Steve Exstance_3\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_3-1536x2304.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_3-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_3-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_3-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_3-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_3-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_3-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /></a><figcaption>Steve testing Leftys in the Cannondale facilities </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_1-scaled.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"2304\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_1-1536x2304.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_1-1536x2304.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_1-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_1-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steve-Exstance_1-scaled.jpg 1707w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you’re a Cannondale fanatic or a rider looking to get a peek behind the scenes of World Cup life, this episode is a must-listen! </p>\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n<h3><strong>Want More?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Find every episode of the BikeRumor Podcast on <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/bikerumor-podcast/id1455519558\" target=\"_blank\">Apple Podcasts</a>, <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6CJD6UAmN9OHfttF4e9lx1\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify</a>, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.podbean.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Podbean</a>. Or through <a href=\"https://feed.podbean.com/bikerumor/feed.xml\" target=\"_blank\">RSS</a>, or wherever you listen to podcasts! Hit like, hit subscribe, and hit play! Can’t find it? Let us know which players you use so we can get them up to speed! Let us know who you want us to interview,  <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/podcast/\">use this form</a> to send us your suggestions!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Follow Bikerumor</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep tabs on all the latest bikes, wheels, components, gear, and tech on The World’s Largest Cycling Tech Blog by following us on <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/bikerumor\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\